                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12917708" author="nickmbailey" created="Mon, 4 Oct 2010 18:54:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is an empty check in begin() anyway so no need for the check in StreamOut.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12917762" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 4 Oct 2010 20:57:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is no reason to go through the target node, which is what session.begin will do, when there is nothing to transfer to it.  Attached is an alternate patch that simply skips to session.close when there is nothing to do.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12917792" author="nickmbailey" created="Mon, 4 Oct 2010 21:55:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good to me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12917798" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 4 Oct 2010 22:06:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12917970" author="hudson" created="Tue, 5 Oct 2010 13:25:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra #556 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/556/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra/556/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    fix unbootstrap when no data is present in a transfer range&lt;br/&gt;
patch by jbellis; reviewed by Nick Bailey for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1573&quot; title=&quot;StreamOut fails to start an empty stream&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-1573&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-1573&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
